title: Jerry Garcia Band - 1974-11-27 - Keystone in Berkely, CA   SBD
description:
Jerry Garcia and Merle Saunders (Pre-Legion of Mary)
11-27-1974 
Keystone, Berkeley, CA

The compilation of these two sources completes this show, 
minus a few missing moments in Bossa Martin, which started in late,
and Someday Baby, which had a reel flip, and no patch source exists yet.

source 1-sdb-?- cd>wavelab 6.0>pitch correction,edits
 provices all except first 1:30 of Bossa Martin and last two songs
 * tracks 5 and 6 were the "missing songs" on shnid #89216, included here.
